channel.title: Client Cache Error
channel.description:
Okay my cache downloads from 1-100%, then it says "unable to load/download acercache" and here's the error I get in the cmd: [url=http://gyazo.com/15dd0ab0fed3b31c7e66a1a249185102]15dd0ab0fed3b31c7e66a1a249185102.png[/url]
How can this be fixed.

item.title: Client Cache Error
item.dc:creator: @Bl3nd Bl3nd
item.description:
@Bl3nd wrote:

The file: data.dat is missing. Either look in the directory that is put out in the cmd and see if it is there, if not, see if you can find that folder anywhere (you may have it but not in that path), once you find that file, paste it into the cache path. If you don’t have it, just look for another cache.
